Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:12.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8\fs21\be1}第七回  「信奈上洛」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥戴将军上洛的计划泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军虽然被暗杀了  但是还有弟弟义昭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把义昭奉为新的将军的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就有上洛的大义名分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁被暗杀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了是将军足利义辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义辉公没有被暗杀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是弟弟  是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏的事件应该是将军被暗杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军在千钧一发之际逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妹妹义昭大人一起逃往大陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史要是走向我不知道的岔路的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在价值就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子要从树上掉下来咯  猴子前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我来代替连猴子的智慧都没有了的相良前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发表一个好提案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被织田家抓住的今川义元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有足利家的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有继承将军家的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把今川义元奉为下一任将军上洛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛  不枉我让你加入织田家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上相良前辈并超越他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么织田军开始上洛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中有浅井和六角等强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真够缠人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田和浅井应该结盟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想和浅井为敌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啊  为敌又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怕的是你那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟到处宣扬要结婚了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这里被取消婚事的话就成天下人的笑柄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢  你要是哭着求我  也许可以考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这事就当没发生过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能结婚的话  我就回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当帮帮我  请一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的妹妹嫁给你好了  感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有听说过信奈大人有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有啦  说有就有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是再啰嗦就取消婚事咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪求您妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  信长也有个妹妹的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝世美女  阿市！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  姐姐大人…这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你嫁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始你就是浅井长政的夫人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是欺诈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不被发现就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你可糊弄不了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好了打下美浓就给我美少女作为奖励的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给我的话  我就不干活咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我美少女啦  美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求我这么无聊的事情  你真不要脸啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人拼命的理由  只有那个吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下第一的美少女哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会遵守约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚洗干净给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢  是谁呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我的胸部…那么好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向姐姐撒娇  给100分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良前辈  请对我温柔点哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个都很赞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这里果然应该是要高岭之花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义元妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难  难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是信奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本就对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…为什么我要给猴子糟蹋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要满怀感激地  接受奖励哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是天下第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心  心理准备还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人说要奖励你  猴子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下第一的美少女  宁宁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始就来当猴子大人的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那家伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺诈啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和浅井长政结盟的信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始向南近江进军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了六角承祯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼近了京都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了这个阵容  京都就近在咫尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来看看京都里的美女  结果完全变成荒凉之地了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的就入室抢劫吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三好军的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他们吗  怎么看都像山贼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为幕府倒台了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都已经成了无法之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈让我们来打探是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是想确认今天的日本中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了统治者的国家的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和五右卫门先去收集情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴先生你们请去姬巫女大人所在的大和御所看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女大人是站在大和的顶点的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是创建这个国家的诸神的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人崇拜供奉着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我所在的世界  似乎有微妙的不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子有一种不可思议的气质呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢去袭击御所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会轻易放过你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关白  近卫前久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暗中操纵公家和政治的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些鼠辈已经被砍头…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下贱者的人头谁要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女大人到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你们还是三好三人众  这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堺之豪商  津田宗及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了钱什么都肯做的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易打倒了将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生这种事  连一文都没赚到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨敌退散  南蛮覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统领比叡山的正觉院豪盛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把南蛮人当作仇敌的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从南蛮人手里保护这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须由我们来掌权
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们必须要有姬巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  近卫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你肯出面了啊  弹正
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松永弹正久秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不在乎地反复倒戈和谋反
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战国的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说姬巫女大人是重要的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箕作城也攻下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想到对所有的城池进行同时攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角一定惊呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里有很多优秀的武将嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有空跟他一点点耗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可以说是妙策  95分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良前辈  现在一定为立不了功而不爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  京都那边比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来似乎很混乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在担心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半兵卫和五右卫门也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  解决掉六角去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无法想象这里就是京都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的世界不是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近我  卑贱之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们尝尝必杀奥义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵天丸亦当如此强力剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  西洋修女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金发和巨乳的组合  破坏力太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦是不能通过暴力治愈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起祈祷吧  给予你的敌人爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来好好地爱一下你的敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  我还是第一次骑大洋马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为日本之民  要知道羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:14:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛  我梵天丸也不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找～到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是葡萄牙来的传教士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝·弗洛伊斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相良良晴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬千代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是破坏的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默示录里的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵天丸是也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们真不走运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来京都传教的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时我都在堺的南蛮寺里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来朝廷请求在全国传教的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不过被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒绝了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:15:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他们说西洋人不能靠近御所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想见见姬巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想同样是侍奉神的姬巫女大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终结战乱之世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让国家变得安居乐业
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是神的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那也是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想只要不放弃就会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会让人感觉很幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是对此深信不疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有观音寺城了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气攻下它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还是劝他们来投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为他们会答应的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意投降的话  就放他们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必去追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是让他们逃跑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是符合公主殿下的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事根本是闻所未闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们能成功上洛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要做出无谓的流血牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角那个蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是战至最后一人  拖住织田信奈就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角大人会不会逃到甲贺的深山里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么凄惨也该有个限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统治着越前的朝仓义景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被称作名门的大大名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让傻瓜公主上洛  这世道也算走到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里将今川义元那样的乡下大名辅佐为将军  才是原本的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要得到那位公主  并添加到余的作品中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兴趣还真是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是哪里的笨蛋让足利将军的妹妹逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想愚弄我们吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是有意见的话  就把越前七十五万石的朝仓当作对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内讧可没有任何好处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三好和朝仓  再加上武田和上杉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能形成信奈包围网了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完成这个是需要花时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈上洛的速度应该更快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且先撤兵  在京都周围燃起大火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈花时间灭火的话  余的士兵和武田、上杉家就能赶过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就交给你们了  三好三人众
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要由我们来迎击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有松永弹正
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军要拼死与信奈战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余也会伸出援手的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对信奈恨之入骨的男人  也来助一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是京都最糟糕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想亲眼看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论百姓如何悲叹痛苦  不出来看一看是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暂且不说未来  这个地狱是现在真实存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  她知道我是来自未来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百姓们能够欢声笑语的世界会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何能够断言？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有织田信奈在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈夺取天下之后  会创造一个崭新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田信奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都欢笑着  和弗洛伊斯姐姐一样的西洋人做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都能和平生活的世界  信奈一定能创造出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是信奈的梦想吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈的梦想也是大家的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  只要不放弃的话  梦想终会成真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头…头有点晕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松永弹正  前来迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来带我回去的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就当作是你被无礼之徒强行带着到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准对他们动手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老老实实跟你回去  这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了  相良氏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五右卫门  半兵卫妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个气息…是被鬼魂什么的袭击了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的送到这里就行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不可思议的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住在这里的巫女吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴  这次玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕由衷地表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…巫女殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  织田信奈终于完成了上洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都成为织田家所统治的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你说的  我让京都的治安恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像相当严重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这样应该就会好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做了应该做的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕的地方还有很多很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我夺取天下之前罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造一个和平的国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:35.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ  時代の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:40.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}立たされて  戸惑う時に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:46.11,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を引いてくれた人へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:50.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}出来ること探した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:55.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つきながら  笑う姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:00.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の裏  涙が見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:06.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}救い求める声  聴き取れるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}許された者だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:17.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}数え切れぬ  嵐を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:23.31,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの闇  裂くヒカリになる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:28.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう  迷わない  ともに生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:33.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誓う夢が  どんな無謀であっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:43.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おぼえていて  信じられる場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:47.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにあると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:35.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只是深陷时代纷争的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:40.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无奈伫立  独自彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:46.11,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在寻觅着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:50.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生命中不可或缺的那个他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:55.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}坚韧的外表  寂寞的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:00.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}掩藏不住内心幽然泪下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:06.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛能聆听到救赎之音的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有寻觅着的他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:17.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}经历风花雪月的洗礼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:23.31,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}方知孤影的你似流光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:28.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不再犹豫  愿与你同存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:33.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算誓言之梦的前方是一片迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:43.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}请记住  属于你的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:47.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在此处
